# Supabase SQL｜TradePilot AI 数据库配置

## 1. product_history 表

请在 Supabase SQL Editor 中执行以下 SQL：

```sql
create table if not exists public.product_history (
  id uuid primary key default gen_random_uuid(),
  user_id uuid not null references auth.users(id) on delete cascade,
  product_name text not null default '未命名产品',
  category text default '未分类',
  score numeric default 0,
  advice text,
  price text,
  competitor_price text,
  product jsonb default '{}'::jsonb,
  result jsonb default '{}'::jsonb,
  report text,
  created_at timestamptz not null default now()
);
```

---

## 2. 开启 RLS

```sql
alter table public.product_history enable row level security;
```

---

## 3. 用户只能读取自己的产品记录

```sql
create policy "Users can read own product history"
on public.product_history
for select
to authenticated
using (auth.uid() = user_id);
```

---

## 4. 用户只能插入自己的产品记录

```sql
create policy "Users can insert own product history"
on public.product_history
for insert
to authenticated
with check (auth.uid() = user_id);
```

---

## 5. 用户只能更新自己的产品记录

```sql
create policy "Users can update own product history"
on public.product_history
for update
to authenticated
using (auth.uid() = user_id)
with check (auth.uid() = user_id);
```

---

## 6. 用户只能删除自己的产品记录

```sql
create policy "Users can delete own product history"
on public.product_history
for delete
to authenticated
using (auth.uid() = user_id);
```

---

## 7. 推荐索引

```sql
create index if not exists product_history_user_created_idx
on public.product_history (user_id, created_at desc);
```

---

## 8. 字段说明

| 字段 | 说明 |
|---|---|
| id | 产品记录 ID |
| user_id | 当前登录用户 ID |
| product_name | 商品名称 |
| category | 商品品类 |
| score | 爆款潜力综合评分 |
| advice | 进货建议 |
| price | 预计售价 |
| competitor_price | 竞品价格 |
| product | 商品表单完整信息 JSON |
| result | 分析结果 JSON |
| report | 完整进货报告文本 |
| created_at | 保存时间 |
